text: The F-14 Tomcat is a fighter plane made for the American Navy. It first flew in 1970 and started to replace the F-4 Phantom II in 1973. It could carry 6 of AIM-54 Phoenix missiles and two AIM-9 Sidewinders. The plane can go supersonic and has variable-sweep wings. In 2006, the Navy stopped using it. Iran uses the F-14, but they are rumored to be in poor condition. ==Related pages== *F/A-18 Hornet *F-15 Eagle *F-16 Fighting Falcon *F-4 Phantom II Category:United States Navy aircraft F-14 Category:Military of Iran
